{"id": "43133", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43133", "title": "Lassal the Flame-spun", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt;, and a member of the &lt;a href=\"Wrathborne\"&gt;Wrathborne&lt;/a&gt;. \nBiography.\nThe Flame-spun yearns to walk through a world reduced to lifeless rubble by his own hand, and indulge in the lingering terror of its incineration. Lassal was born of the primal fear of extinction, and is so eager and enthusiastic to witness it that he may become as much of a danger to the other Wrathborne as he is to their victims.\nWrathborne Invasion.\nIn a vision of the future granted by the &lt;a href=\"Einfrinn%20Tree\"&gt;Einfrinn Tree&lt;/a&gt;, Lassal invaded &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt; alongside the Wrathborne. Directed by &lt;a href=\"Izilech%20the%20Mishappen\"&gt;Izilech the Mishappen&lt;/a&gt;, he set the city ablaze, and slaughtered anyone in his way. At the vision's end, he defeated &lt;a href=\"the%20Shard-seeker\"&gt;the Shard-seeker&lt;/a&gt; who were having the vision.\nThe Shard-seeker later used the Einfrinn Tree to fight Lassal in &lt;a href=\"Scorched%20Hellscape\"&gt;his lair&lt;/a&gt;. After his defeat, Lassal's &lt;a href=\"Flame-twisted%20Claw\"&gt;hand&lt;/a&gt; was severed and used by the &lt;a href=\"Helliquary\"&gt;Helliquary&lt;/a&gt;.\nEve of Unmaking.\nC.&lt;a href=\"timeline%231273\"&gt;1273&lt;/a&gt;, Lassal had reformed in Hell. He\u2014along with &lt;a href=\"Iscea\"&gt;two&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Yamnaal\"&gt;other&lt;/a&gt; demons led a &lt;a href=\"vanguard\"&gt;vanguard&lt;/a&gt; force to invade the &lt;a href=\"Lidwinter%20Woods\"&gt;Lidwinter Woods&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nLassal appears in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". He is a &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; in the \"&lt;a href=\"Opening%20the%20Helliquary\"&gt;Opening the Helliquary&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;, and later appears as a boss in the game's &lt;a href=\"Helliquary\"&gt;Helliquary&lt;/a&gt; system, where he is fought in the &lt;a href=\"Scorched%20Hellscape\"&gt;Scorched Hellscape&lt;/a&gt;. He has the following attacks:\nPhase 2.\nLassal leaps to the center of the arena and changes to his true form.\nUpon defeat, he drops the &lt;a href=\"Flame-twisted%20Claw\"&gt;Flame-twisted Claw&lt;/a&gt;. Defeating Lassal is required to unlocking &lt;a href=\"Hell%20%28difficulty%29\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt; I difficulty."}
