{"id": "11366", "revid": "47915220", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11366", "title": "Level 12 (Diablo I)", "text": "Level 12 is the fourth and the last Caves-style level in the original \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20%28Game%29\"&gt;Diablo&lt;/a&gt;\", and logically the hardest. \nThe player(s) reaches Level 12 after from a stairway in &lt;a href=\"Level%2011%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 11&lt;/a&gt;. Somewhere in Level 12 there is a stairway to &lt;a href=\"Level%2013%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 13&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt's also the third and final level (after &lt;a href=\"Level%201%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 1&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Level%2011%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 11&lt;/a&gt;) where there is no quest related to the level.\nBestiary.\nThis level often already gives a show of what will be waiting in &lt;a href=\"Hell%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt; for there can be monster classes like &lt;a href=\"Black%20Knight\"&gt;Black Knight&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Succubus\"&gt;Succubus&lt;/a&gt;. It introduces the player(s) to powerful monsters that resists and/or are immune to the magic types, including some that even start casting Lightning spells constantly at the player(s) and some that throw Firebolt-like balls at the player(s).\nThe following monsters can be found in Level 12:"}
{"id": "11354", "revid": "47915220", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11354", "title": "Level 13 (Diablo I)", "text": "Level 13 is the first &lt;a href=\"Hell%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt;-style level in the original \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20%28Game%29\"&gt;Diablo&lt;/a&gt;\". The player(s) reaches Level 13 after from a stairway in &lt;a href=\"Level%2012%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 12&lt;/a&gt;. Somewhere in Level 13 there is a stairway to &lt;a href=\"Level%2014%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 14&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpon entering Level 13, the character mentions, \"I must be getting close\".\nOverall, this level represents a clear step up in difficulty. From this level &lt;a href=\"Animals\"&gt;Animals&lt;/a&gt; are reduced to very low numbers.\nQuests.\nIf available, the following quest can be done or initiated in Level 13:\nBestiary.\nThe following monsters can be found in Level 13:"}
