{"id": "12863", "revid": "47915220", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12863", "title": "Level 15 (Diablo I)", "text": "Level 15\u00a0is the third\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Hell%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt;-style level in the original\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20%28Game%29\"&gt;Diablo&lt;/a&gt;\".\u00a0The player(s) reach(es) Level 15 from a stairway in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Level%2014%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 14&lt;/a&gt;. Somewhere in Level 15, there is a weapon rack that contains\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Staff%20of%20Lazarus\"&gt;Lazarus' staff&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and starts the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Archbishop%20Lazarus%20%28Quest%29\"&gt;Archbishop Lazarus&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0quest,\u00a0which will upon completing enable your character to enter &lt;a href=\"Level%2016%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 16&lt;/a&gt;.\nBestiary.\nThis area has the lowest monster variety of all random levels, and has monsters exclusive only to it (&lt;a href=\"Azure%20Drake\"&gt;Azure Drake&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Succubus\"&gt;Soul Burner&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Cabalist\"&gt;Cabalist&lt;/a&gt;). This level also shares lowest Unique number in random levels with &lt;a href=\"Level%2011%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Level 11&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe following monsters can be found in Level 15:"}
