{"id": "6465", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6465", "title": "Lidless Wall (Diablo II)", "text": "Lidless Wall is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Grim%20Shield\"&gt;Grim Shield&lt;/a&gt; from \"\".\nDue to the nature of its skills, Lidless Wall is most likely better suited in the hands of a spellcaster than a physical fighter.\nIn fact, Lidless Wall is probably the best unique &lt;a href=\"shields\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; for spellcasters (not including &lt;a href=\"Rune%20Words\"&gt;Rune Words&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;Set Items&lt;/a&gt;, which have plenty of caster-friendly shields). Besides its boost to all skills, Lidless Wall also gives a variety of bonuses that benefit magic users.\nPerhaps most notable is Lidless Wall's increase to maximum &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Energy\"&gt;Energy&lt;/a&gt;, and its &lt;a href=\"Faster%20Cast%20Rate\"&gt;Faster Cast Rate&lt;/a&gt;. These properties are highly valued among spellcasters (particularly &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt;es and &lt;a href=\"Bonemancer\"&gt;Bonemancer&lt;/a&gt;s), as the Lidless Wall can be held with an &lt;a href=\"Orbs\"&gt;Orb&lt;/a&gt; or in the other hand.\nHowever, the biggest problem with Lidless Wall is its lack of &lt;a href=\"Resistances\"&gt;Resistances&lt;/a&gt;, which are often sought after in shields especially in and &lt;a href=\"Difficulty\"&gt;difficulties&lt;/a&gt;. This can be partially remedied by socketing Lidless Wall with the &lt;a href=\"Lord%20of%20Destruction%20%28Act%29\"&gt;Act V&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Siege%20on%20Harrogath%20%28Quest%29\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; and inserting a perfect &lt;a href=\"Diamond\"&gt;Diamond&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0or &lt;a href=\"Um%20Rune\"&gt;Um Rune&lt;/a&gt;, but otherwise Lidless Wall is lacking defensively compared to other shields.\nStats.\nDefense: 271-347 \nRequired Level: 41\nRequired Strength: 58\nDurability: 70\nChance to Block:\nPaladin &lt;a href=\"Smite\"&gt;Smite&lt;/a&gt; Damage: 14 To 20"}
{"id": "20816", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20816", "title": "Lidless Wall (Diablo III)", "text": "The Lidless Wall is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"shields\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 50 to drop.\nIt is one of the few shields with any practical bonuses for ranged classes. It is also one of the two shields that can provide additional elemental skill damage (the other being &lt;a href=\"Hallowed%20Barricade\"&gt;Hallowed Barricade&lt;/a&gt;), and the only non-&lt;a href=\"Crusader\"&gt;Crusader&lt;/a&gt; shield that can increase maximum resources. Prior to patch 2.1, it also granted bonus &lt;a href=\"attack%20speed\"&gt;attack speed&lt;/a&gt; and resource cost reduction.\nThis is one of the few items with 5 Primary affixes."}
