{"id": "16326", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16326", "title": "Light (magic suffix)", "text": "Light is a &lt;a href=\"Suffix%20%28Diablo%20II%29\"&gt;Suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It provides a small bonus to both &lt;a href=\"Light%20Radius\"&gt;Light Radius&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Attack%20Rating\"&gt;Attack Rating&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can start appearing on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 1, but is only capable of reaching full effect with all items at level 6.\nThe base Light Radius is 13. The Max Light Radius you can have is 18, so anything more than net +5 to Light Radius will not matter.\nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;Amulets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Body%20Armor\"&gt;Body Armor&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rings\"&gt;Rings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Scepters\"&gt;Scepters&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;Staves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Wands\"&gt;Wands&lt;/a&gt;"}
