{"id": "38615", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38615", "title": "Lightning (Diablo IV)", "text": "Lightning\u00a0is a Destruction Lightning spell used by\u00a0\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\". It resembles the &lt;a href=\"Electrocute\"&gt;Electrocute&lt;/a&gt; spell more than other versions of &lt;a href=\"Lightning\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn-game.\nUnlike the previous versions, Lightning does not &lt;a href=\"Piercing\"&gt;pierce&lt;/a&gt; and does not do random damage anymore, but instead works as a weakened variant of , bouncing from foe to foe, weakening with each jump. The number of bounces increases with the spell rank.\nTo compensate, it does not cost any &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt; to cast, unlike the Chain Lightning, and has no &lt;a href=\"cooldown\"&gt;cooldown&lt;/a&gt;."}
