{"id": "2161", "revid": "154566", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2161", "title": "Lightning (skill)", "text": "Lightning is a &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Skill\"&gt;Skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\n\"This spell allows a Sorceress to summon the very power of the heavens and emit a tremendous surge of electrical energy. Creating a channel of lightning directed at her target, she cuts a swath through her opponents with pinpoint accuracy. \"\nGeneral Information.\nSynergies.\nWith synergies in account, Lightning is the most powerful of the Sorceress' &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20Spells\"&gt;Lightning Spells&lt;/a&gt;, even more so than &lt;a href=\"Thunder%20Storm\"&gt;Thunder Storm&lt;/a&gt;. However, its maximum and minimum damage varies wildly. \nLightning is the spell of choice for most enemies skilled in lightning-type spells, such as &lt;a href=\"Mephisto\"&gt;Mephisto&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Ghost\"&gt;Ghost&lt;/a&gt;s. The spell shoots a &lt;a href=\"piercing\"&gt;piercing&lt;/a&gt; lightning bolt in a straight line, and thus is less accurate than Chain Lightning. However, this is compensated for with its greater destructive potential."}
