{"id": "52852", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52852", "title": "Varyana", "text": "Varyana is a &lt;a href=\"mercenary\"&gt;mercenary&lt;/a&gt;, and member of the &lt;a href=\"Pale%20Hand\"&gt;Pale Hand&lt;/a&gt;. Varyana wields brutal hand-to-hand weapons that are her instruments of carnage; those that come within her grasp fall swiftly. \nVaryana is the cook of the Pale Hand.\nBiography.\nA former &lt;a href=\"Cannibals\"&gt;cannibal&lt;/a&gt; who left her tribe when they started dealing with darker forces, Varyana is a butcher by trade, turned mercenary.\nIn-game.\nVaryana is a hirable mercenary in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", introduced in the \"&lt;a href=\"Vessel%20of%20Hatred\"&gt;Vessel of Hatred&lt;/a&gt;\" expansion. She is axe-wielder that yanks multiple enemies from afar and slashes at enemies.\nVaryana has a Massacre meter which grows in strength the longer blood feeds her blades and scales off the killstreak. The meter is fed by the player killing &lt;a href=\"monster\"&gt;monster&lt;/a&gt;s. The meter activates after the player kills ten monsters in a single encounter. The meter is divided into a number of thresholds, and after each threshold, the player's &lt;a href=\"movement%20speed\"&gt;movement speed&lt;/a&gt; increases.\nAbilities.\nVaryana's skill tree is split into two themes\u2014dual-wield axes, and large mace. \nDevelopment.\nVaryana's Massacre meter is a partial revival of the &lt;a href=\"Kill%20Counter\"&gt;Kill Counter&lt;/a&gt; feature in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
