{"id": "46207", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46207", "title": "Veszta", "text": "Veszta was a resident of the &lt;a href=\"Razed%20Village\"&gt;Razed Village&lt;/a&gt; before it was destroyed and overrun by &lt;a href=\"khazra\"&gt;khazra&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nVeszta was a resident of the Razed Village. She was a close friend, and secret lover of Eperke the village's jeweler. &lt;a href=\"Eperke\"&gt;Eperke&lt;/a&gt; regularly gave her gifts in the form of jewelry, amongst which was a beautiful ring. At a point she noticed that &lt;a href=\"Tarkal\"&gt;Tarkal&lt;/a&gt;; the village's misfit, had been staring at her and Eperke; especially at her ring, whenever they cross paths. This seriously creeped her out. One day she discovered that her ring had been stolen. Though she didn't have proof, she suspected Tarkal. Eperke tried to console her, even promising to replace the ring. That night she decided to sleep in her cellar in order to feel safer. Unfortunately, khazra attacked the village the next morning. Veszta died in her cellar, trapped under rubble and choking on smoke.\nIn-game.\nVeszta is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; briefly seen in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". She is the final boss of the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt;; \"&lt;a href=\"More%20Than%20Love\"&gt;More Than Love&lt;/a&gt;\". At the end of the quest her spirit passes on after the player returns her ring to her resting place."}
