{"id": "5745", "revid": "154566", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5745", "title": "Vidala's Barb", "text": "Vidala's Barb is a &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Long%20Battle%20Bow\"&gt;long battle bow&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is one of the four pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Vidala%27s%20Rig\"&gt;Vidala's Rig&lt;/a&gt; item set.\nIt is considered obsolete past the early stages of the game due to its low base damage and slow attack speed.\nStats.\nTwo Hand Damage: 3 to 18 \nRequired &lt;a href=\"Dexterity\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;: 50\nRequired &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;: 40\nRequired Level: 14\n (2 items)"}
{"id": "5746", "revid": "55391664", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5746", "title": "Vidala's Fetlock", "text": "Vidala's Fetlock are &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Light%20Plated%20Boots\"&gt;light plated boots&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". They are one of the four pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Vidala%27s%20Rig\"&gt;Vidala's Rig&lt;/a&gt; item set. Their decent increase to &lt;a href=\"Movement%20Speed\"&gt;Movement Speed&lt;/a&gt; and their increase to maximum stamina make them useful for low level characters, though higher level characters usually have little use for increased maximum stamina and may elect to use other boots with more benefits. \nStats.\nDefense: 9-11\nDurability: 18\nRequired Strength: 50\nRequired Level: 14\nAssassin Kick Damage: 8-16\n (2 items)\nTrivia.\nA fetlock is a part of a horse's leg. Given the great +150 boost to stamina, it would appear to be aptly named."}
