{"id": "48534", "revid": "2011810", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48534", "title": "Vigil of Blades", "text": "Vigil of Blades is a PvP event in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Cycle%20of%20Strife\"&gt;Cycle of Strife&lt;/a&gt;.\nGameplay.\nVigil of Blades uses the &lt;a href=\"Alley%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Alley of Blood&lt;/a&gt; battle format and has 12 separate 8v8 battles similarly to &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20War\"&gt;Shadow War&lt;/a&gt;.\nVigil of Blades happens on the first 3 weeks of an &lt;a href=\"Immortals\"&gt;Immortal&lt;/a&gt; reign. The 3 Immortal clans are matched up against the top 3 Shadow clans. Each pairing contributes 1 point to the faction. The faction that wins more of the 3 matchups gains a cumulative +4% Life and Damage buff during &lt;a href=\"Rite%20of%20Exile\"&gt;Rite of Exile&lt;/a&gt; for the rest of the reign."}
{"id": "21346", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21346", "title": "Vigilance", "text": "Vigilance is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"polearms\"&gt;polearm&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 60 to drop.\nThis weapon is &lt;a href=\"Monk\"&gt;Monk&lt;/a&gt;-oriented, but any class may benefit from an unmodified &lt;a href=\"Inner%20Sanctuary\"&gt;Inner Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt; (which is on a separate &lt;a href=\"cooldown\"&gt;cooldown&lt;/a&gt; and benefits from runes and enhancements). The chance is quite low (about 10%)."}
