{"id": "49328", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49328", "title": "Voszalko", "text": "Voszalko is a member of the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20Light\"&gt;Cathedral of Light&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nVoszalko arrived (or was born) in &lt;a href=\"Kyovashad\"&gt;Kyovashad&lt;/a&gt; c. &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231286\"&gt;1286&lt;/a&gt;. He joined the Cathedral of Light and had a high opinion of his standing within the church.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231336\"&gt;1336&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Iosef\"&gt;Iosef&lt;/a&gt; told Voszalko about , how they had ingested the &lt;a href=\"blood\"&gt;blood&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Lilith\"&gt;Lilith&lt;/a&gt;. When the &lt;a href=\"Knights%20Penitent\"&gt;Knights Penitent&lt;/a&gt; marched on &lt;a href=\"Burning%20Hells\"&gt;Hell&lt;/a&gt;, he remained in the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20Light%20%28Fractured%20Peaks%29\"&gt;Cathedral&lt;/a&gt; to \"keep the faith.\"\nAfter the &lt;a href=\"death\"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Inarius\"&gt;Inarius&lt;/a&gt;, the Cathedral gained new recruits, who were ignorant of Voszalko's (supposed) status.\nBlood of the Mother.\nAt some point after Inarius's death, Voszalko confronted the Wanderer in &lt;a href=\"Kyovashad\"&gt;Kyovashad&lt;/a&gt;. He told them that Lilith's blood would eat them from within, and to head to &lt;a href=\"Nevesk\"&gt;Nevesk&lt;/a&gt; to see the truth. There, the Wanderer found a &lt;a href=\"blood%20petal\"&gt;blood petal&lt;/a&gt;, and Voszalko presented it as proof that Lilith had sullied them. He offered them an exorcism, and ordered them to find &lt;a href=\"the%20Child%27s%20Caul\"&gt;the Child's Caul&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Mercy%27s%20Reach\"&gt;Mercy's Reach&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe Wanderer returned to Kyovashad where they presented the Caul to Voszalko. He told them to meet him in the &lt;a href=\"Elysiuma%20Archives\"&gt;Elysiuma Archives&lt;/a&gt; inside the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20Light%20%28Fractured%20Peaks%29\"&gt;Cathedral of Light&lt;/a&gt;. \nInside, Voszalko attempted his exorcism, accompanied by a group of &lt;a href=\"Knights%20Penitent\"&gt;Knights Penitent&lt;/a&gt;. However, something went wrong; apparently the Wanderer blacked out and killed the knights. Shaken, Voszalko begged the Wanderer to leave.\nIn-game.\nVoszalko is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\". He can be found in &lt;a href=\"Kyovashad\"&gt;Kyovashad&lt;/a&gt; and initiates the \"&lt;a href=\"Blood%20of%20the%20Mother\"&gt;Blood of the Mother&lt;/a&gt;.\" He was added at some point during \"&lt;a href=\"Season%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Season of Blood&lt;/a&gt;\", and players must have completed the game's main campaign to access the quest."}
