{"id": "26581", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26581", "title": "Wall of Man", "text": "The\u00a0Wall of Man\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Craftable%20items\"&gt;crafted&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"shields\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It\u00a0requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 70 to be worn. The level 23 crafted equivalent is the &lt;a href=\"Wall%20of%20Bone\"&gt;Wall of Bone&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe special affix is a 20% reduction in all damage taken for 5 seconds, with a 10 seconds cooldown.\nCrafting.\nThe Wall of Bone can be crafted using the\u00a0Plan: Wall of Man, 64000 &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt;, 20 &lt;a href=\"Reusable%20Parts\"&gt;Reusable Parts&lt;/a&gt;, 20 &lt;a href=\"Arcane%20Dust\"&gt;Arcane Dust&lt;/a&gt;, 30 &lt;a href=\"Veiled%20Crystal\"&gt;Veiled Crystal&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Khanduran%20Rune\"&gt;Khanduran Rune&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Arreat%20War%20Tapestry\"&gt;Arreat War Tapestry&lt;/a&gt;.\nPrior to Patch 2.0.6., it also required one &lt;a href=\"Human%20Cartilage\"&gt;Human Cartilage&lt;/a&gt;, which only dropped from the unique &lt;a href=\"Unburied\"&gt;Unburied&lt;/a&gt;."}
