{"id": "21119", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21119", "title": "Telranden's Hand", "text": "Telranden's Hand is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"mace\"&gt;mace&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 29 to drop.\nIt is the only Legendary mace with no noteworthy Magic Properties. It may be seen as equivalent to a &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Item\"&gt;Rare Item&lt;/a&gt; with a guarantee of 6 properties."}
