{"id": "6511", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6511", "title": "Templar's Might", "text": "Templar's Might is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Armor\"&gt;Sacred Armor&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIts bonus to &lt;a href=\"Stamina\"&gt;Stamina&lt;/a&gt; is of little use, since most &lt;a href=\"Classes\"&gt;characters&lt;/a&gt; will have leveled &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; up sufficiently by the time they can use Templar's Might. However, it provides fantastic defense against &lt;a href=\"missiles\"&gt;missiles&lt;/a&gt;, as well as a skill boost directed to &lt;a href=\"Paladin\"&gt;Paladin&lt;/a&gt;s.\nStats.\nDefense: 1622-1923\nRequired Level: 74\nRequired Strength: 232\nDurability: 60"}
