{"id": "21083", "revid": "191061", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21083", "title": "The Barber", "text": "The Barber is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Ceremonial%20Knife\"&gt;Ceremonial Knife&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=\"dagger\"&gt;dagger&lt;/a&gt; prior to patch 2.5.0) in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 14 to drop.\nThis dagger used to increase &lt;a href=\"Critical%20Hit\"&gt;Critical Hit&lt;/a&gt; Damage prior to 2.5.0, which is normally not allowed on a weapon. Prior to patch 2.4.3, it also rolled five Primary affixes.\nAs of 2.4.3, it gained a unique affix: &lt;a href=\"Spirit%20Barrage\"&gt;Spirit Barrage&lt;/a&gt; no longer deals damage on impact, but instead accumulates it until the casting is stopped for any reason. Once it happens, \"all\" affected enemies \"each\" explode for up to 500% of \"full\" accumulated damage to all nearby foes (and themselves), with possible interlapping.\nFor the Phantasm rune, the \"stop casting\" moment is the time when they expire, detonating all enemies they attacked over the duration.\nThe Manitou rune will trigger the explosion when enough damage has accumulated to kill the target."}
{"id": "26543", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26543", "title": "The Barracks", "text": "The Barracks is a two-level dungeon that can spawn in &lt;a href=\"The%20Battlefields\"&gt;The Battlefields&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Act%20III%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act III&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It shares the same location as the &lt;a href=\"Fortified%20Bunker\"&gt;Fortified Bunker&lt;/a&gt;, very close to the waypoint, before exiting the barricaded section into the battlefield proper. It is built directly into the &lt;a href=\"Bastion%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Bastion's Keep&lt;/a&gt; structure.\nIt is notable for having a chance to contain the &lt;a href=\"Mysterious%20Chest\"&gt;Mysterious Barrel&lt;/a&gt;, which drops &lt;a href=\"Mace%20of%20the%20Crows\"&gt;Mace of the Crows&lt;/a&gt;.\nA &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt; may be available to clear the second level of the dungeon. The &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Ties\"&gt;Blood Ties&lt;/a&gt; event also takes place there, and may be available at the same time, in which case both can be completed at once."}
