{"id": "33712", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33712", "title": "The Bound Shaman", "text": "The Bound Shaman is a special in &lt;a href=\"Adventure%20Mode\"&gt;Adventure Mode&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It can only appear if nominated a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt;, in any zone of any &lt;a href=\"Act\"&gt;Act&lt;/a&gt;. If it appears, one can go through a red &lt;a href=\"portal\"&gt;portal&lt;/a&gt; and access any of the special bounty zones: &lt;a href=\"Leoric%27s%20Gardens\"&gt;Leoric's Gardens&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Blighted%20Sewer\"&gt;Blighted Sewer&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Killing%20Grounds\"&gt;The Killing Grounds&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Archives\"&gt;The Archives&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Bound%20Keep\"&gt;The Bound Keep&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Nephalem%20Proving%20Ground\"&gt;Nephalem Proving Ground&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe event itself requires cleansing a &lt;a href=\"Cursed%20Chest\"&gt;Cursed Chest&lt;/a&gt;. Once it is touched, a timer will start, and a huge horde of &lt;a href=\"Fallen\"&gt;Fallen&lt;/a&gt; will appear. Among the s and &lt;a href=\"Fallen%20Overseer\"&gt;Fallen Overseer&lt;/a&gt;s, there will also be 6 s. Killing all the Fallen ends the event. All Shamans must be killed before time is up to receive a bonus &lt;a href=\"Radiant%20Chest\"&gt;Radiant Chest&lt;/a&gt;."}
