{"id": "6290", "revid": "26096179", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6290", "title": "The Cat's Eye", "text": "The Cat's Eye is a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;amulet&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAny physical fighter (but especially &lt;a href=\"Bowazon\"&gt;Bowazon&lt;/a&gt;s) could benefit from the &lt;a href=\"Dexterity\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt; bonus The Cat's Eye gives, as it not only boosts Attack Rating but gives a great bonus to Defense. Additionally, The Cat's Eye increases Attack Speed, which can make an already fast weapon even faster. It also boasts increased &lt;a href=\"Defense%20vs.%20Missiles\"&gt;Defense vs. Missiles&lt;/a&gt;, which is particularly useful when compounded with similar equipment such as &lt;a href=\"Shaftstop\"&gt;Shaftstop&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Carrion%20Wind\"&gt;Carrion Wind&lt;/a&gt;. The Faster Run/Walk this amulet offers is also a good affix for a variety of situations, be it running to/from enemies or trying to catch up to an ally needing help as quickly as possible.\nStats.\nRequired Level: 50"}
{"id": "24959", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=24959", "title": "The Cave Under the Well", "text": "The Cave Under the Well is a small \"dungeon\" zone that can appear in &lt;a href=\"Old%20Tristram%20Road\"&gt;Old Tristram Road&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Act%20I%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act I&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". As the name indicates, it is a watery cave accessed by going down a well on the side of the road.\nA few coins are scattered on the floor, and some minor chests or other containers can be found in it. The monster population is sparse, but several &lt;a href=\"Risen\"&gt;Risen&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Walking%20Corpse\"&gt;Walking Corpse&lt;/a&gt;s will be around. This side zone doesn't feature much, but it needs to be explored to get the achievement\u00a0&lt;a href=\"No%20Stone%20Unturned\"&gt;No Stone Unturned&lt;/a&gt;."}
