ven over to the demons, who have tortured him in the Hells ever since. Most of Inarius's followers were killed; those who remained shared an even &lt;a href=\"Overlord\"&gt;darker fate&lt;/a&gt;. Despite the tragedy, I believe the nephalem may yet play a part in resolving the Eternal Conflict. - Archangel Auriel\""}
