{"id": "20767", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20767", "title": "The Crudest Boots", "text": "The Crudest Boots are &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"boots\"&gt;boots&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". They require &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 8 to drop.\nThe unique affix added in patch 2.1 summons two &lt;a href=\"Mystic%20Ally\"&gt;Mystic Allies&lt;/a&gt; at once. They will both perform empowered attacks when activated, and both active and passive bonuses to the &lt;a href=\"Monk\"&gt;Monk&lt;/a&gt;'s own attributes will also be doubled. The two Allies will also be useful for the &lt;a href=\"Unity%20%28Skill%29\"&gt;Unity&lt;/a&gt; skill and, most importantly, for &lt;a href=\"Inna%27s%20Mantra\"&gt;Inna's Mantra&lt;/a&gt;. The latter, if coupled with these boots, will summon 10 Mystic Allies instead of 5, with all respective benefits."}
