{"id": "33633", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33633", "title": "The Cursed Shrines", "text": "The Cursed Shrines is a special in &lt;a href=\"Adventure%20Mode\"&gt;Adventure Mode&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It can only appear if nominated a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt;, in any zone of any &lt;a href=\"Act\"&gt;Act&lt;/a&gt;. If it appears, one can go through a red &lt;a href=\"portal\"&gt;portal&lt;/a&gt; and access one of the special bounty zones: &lt;a href=\"Leoric%27s%20Gardens\"&gt;Leoric's Gardens&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Blighted%20Sewer\"&gt;Blighted Sewer&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Killing%20Grounds\"&gt;The Killing Grounds&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Archives\"&gt;The Archives&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"The%20Bound%20Keep\"&gt;The Bound Keep&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Nephalem%20Proving%20Ground\"&gt;Nephalem Proving Ground&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe event itself requires cleansing a &lt;a href=\"Cursed%20Chest\"&gt;Cursed Chest&lt;/a&gt;. Once the area is entered, a timer will start, and 6 Cursed will appear throughout the arena. Each will be cleansed and disappear (without granting any Shrine effects) when touched, but will also spawn a large pack of monsters of random type, and cast one random monster affix. All six must be touched before time is up, then remaining monsters cleared, to receive a bonus &lt;a href=\"Radiant%20Chest\"&gt;Radiant Chest&lt;/a&gt;.\nInterestingly, each Shrine \"will\" benefit from &lt;a href=\"Nemesis%20Bracers\"&gt;Nemesis Bracers&lt;/a&gt;, if the character has them, and will summon a Rare pack."}
{"id": "29449", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=29449", "title": "The Cursed War Room", "text": " \nThe Cursed War Room is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Cursed%20Chest\"&gt;Cursed Chest&lt;/a&gt; event in &lt;a href=\"Act%20V%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act V&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Pandemonium%20Fortress\"&gt;Pandemonium Fortress&lt;/a&gt; on Level 1, where the primary enemy is the &lt;a href=\"Winged%20Assassin\"&gt;Winged Assassin&lt;/a&gt;. The event, much like most other events, is randomized; it may not be seen in some games. It's possible for this event to be a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt;."}
