{"id": "7003", "revid": "26096179", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7003", "title": "The Deflector", "text": "The Deflector is quite useful at low levels but fairly mediocre at best, like all &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Items\"&gt;Unique&lt;/a&gt; shields but the &lt;a href=\"Stormshield%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Stormshield&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis item can never be found in Multiplayer \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20I\"&gt;Diablo I&lt;/a&gt;\", since the &lt;a href=\"Split%20Skull%20Shield\"&gt;Split Skull Shield&lt;/a&gt; will always drop instead. It can be found in Single Player, but only in a game in which you find two Unique Bucklers, of which The Deflector will be the second."}
